Events.Text: Say hello to the AI assistant and ask for help (see instructions on the left). [instruction 1 of 6]
Hello, I need to make an appointment with Dr. Johnson today
Try to get an appointment as soon as possible (right now it is 1 pm on Monday). [instruction 2 of 6]
Hello. What is your name?
Could I have your name, please?
Angela
Keep asking for other times until the assistant has found a slot for you. Engage in smalltalk once this is done. [instruction 3 of 6]
At what time?
At what time can you be at the clinic?
I'd like ASAP, can it be 3PM?
Say something about Dr. Johnson, the AI Assistant, or something that has happened to you today. Be creative! [instruction 4 of 6]
What are your symptoms?
Could you describe your symptoms, please?
For 2 days I've had a fever, runny nose, sneezing, and been tired
It occurs to you that you also want to make an appointment to get your kid Alexis vaccinated. Perhaps you can schedule a second appointment at the same time? [instruction 5 of 6]

Constraints.Symptoms: " fever, runny nose, sneezing, and been tired"
